{"word":"G4792 - συγκομίζω - synkomízō - soong-kom-id'-zo - Carry","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συγκομίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">synkomízō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soong-kom-id'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Carry</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - எடு"},{"paragraph":"1. to carry or bring together, to collect"},{"paragraph":"2. to carry with others, help in carrying out, the dead to be burned or buried to bury"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G2865 - κομίζω - komízō - kom-id'-zo/2865\">G2865</a>; to <i>convey together</i>, that is, <i>collect</i> or <i>bear</i> away in company <i>with</i> others: - carry.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}